font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">要求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港正受人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n公然妨礙新聞自由 警方出公關稿籲媒體跟從<br />\n截斷交通 封鎖去道<br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n威嚇扼殺民主自由現代普世價值<br />\n<br />\n召喚攬炒巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e21cc04fa63016eee638cffcc39e93b198a35ed","tid":1524841,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T23:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8ff052d3622fa935bc9a44d928643ed117ddc9","tid":1524841,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b541cd00dc6a031c42ba40633e613b491641ec","tid":1524841,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit)<br />\n5. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n6. 每星期去連儂貼3張文宣<br />\n7. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n8. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n9. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n10. 不要說推，試著將呢整個訊息copy and paste嚟推post#kill<br />\n11. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。<br />\n<br />\n利申：我做緊。Best effort 。你呢？"},{"pid":"ca6a7b75719f9edeee9fa5606a8477de32ff78f3","tid":1524841,"uid":71233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:28:47.000Z","msg":"twitter 戰線打中英聯合聲明<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533344</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社林鄭單錄音畀哂牌我地, 求大家幫手打香港冇自治, 中英聯合聲明徹底失敗依張牌好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-carrielam-specialre-idUSKCN1VN1DU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-carrielam-specialre-idUSKCN1VN1DU&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70lLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=d98873c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-carrielam-specialre-idUSKCN1VN1DU&h=a3f8abb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-carrielam-specialre-idUSKCN1VN1DU</a><br />\n<br />\n例子:<br />\n<br />\nThe HK Chief Executive admitted that she had no authority to put up a political solution to solve the Hong Kong crisis. <br />\n<br />\nThis has proven a complete failure of the Sino-British Joint Declaration! SOS HK<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKneedyourhelp/status/1168554236474314752?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKneedyourhelp%2Fstatus%2F1168554236474314752%3Fs%3D20&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70lLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=ca255bcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKneedyourhelp%2Fstatus%2F1168554236474314752%3Fs%3D20&h=5f14dbaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKneedyourhelp/status/1168554236474314752?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n我見twitter冇咩人主攻依條戰線, 大家幫幫手！！"},{"pid":"84a1896df4cc3dd642e916251e0f81da8bd7b688","tid":1524841,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n